items.title: Ukraine's borders must not be changed by force, EU leaders say
items.description: The EU says "the people of Ukraine must have the freedom to decide their future."

items.title: Scores still missing a week after India flash floods
items.description: Rescue operations at the disaster site have been hampered by heavy rains and blocked roads.

items.title: Charges dropped against teen pilot detained in Antarctica
items.description: Ethan Guo must leave the island and pay $30,000 dollars to charity for illegally landing on Chilean territory, a judge says.

items.title: Grammy-winning Afropop star Tems: 'Women are not respected in the industry'
items.description: The Nigerian musician details her rise to the top of a notoriously male-dominated industry.

items.title: Man faces jail in US for shipping 850 turtles in socks to Hong Kong
items.description: The turtles were packed in boxes labelled as plastic toys, according to the Justice Department.
